'''
batch_size = 32

train_dataset = tf.data.experimental.make_csv_dataset(
                        train_dataset_fp,
                        batch_size,
                        column_names=column_names,
                        label_name=label_name,
                        num_epochs=1
                    )

'''
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
The make_csv_dataset function returns a tf.data.Dataset of (features, label) pairs, 
